 were in session most of these lost Graduates (RIP) will either be serving their father land or be in a different places or circumstance that might have speared their lives and delay death till another day.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">As \u00a0a Nigerian, and a \u00a0Polytechnic Student I demand these from my President.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\">That ASUP Strike should be called off with immediate effect!</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\">That the President as a matter of urgency, He has a round table with ASUP Like their Counter Part ASUU in order to move Polytechnic education to the next level.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\">That the Dichotomy between HND &amp; BSc be treated as a matter of National urgency.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\">That Polytechnic student should be treated like Nigerian student and not second class citizens.</p>\r\n<p>\u00a0That plans are put in Motion that all quallifed finalists be considered for youth service in the next available Batch after their exams.</p>","targets":[{"name":"FEDERAL GOVERNMENT OF NIGERIA","type":"custom"},{"name":"Federal Government Of Nigeria Ministry of Education","type":"custom"},{"name":"Federal Government Of Nigeria National Assembly","type":"custom"},{"name":"Federal Government of Nigeria Ministry Of Labour","type":"custom"},{"name":"Academic Staff Union of Polytechnics","type":"custom"}],"letter_body":"End ASUP & COESU STRIKE Now","signature_count":9,"image_url":"//d22r54gnmuhwmk.cloudfront.net/app-assets/petitions/show/default_petition-2dea4f8fdd8a3fa93201db8b1c7cf36d.png","category":null,"goal":100,"created_at":"2014-05-03T13:22:03Z","end_at":"2015-05-03T23:59:59Z","creator_name":"ugo uduh","creator_url":"http://api.change.org/u/91531970","organization_name":null,"organization_url":null}